#: _versions/3.34/guides/spring-web.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When using the Quarkus Spring Web compatibility layer on top of the reactive stack (`quarkus-rest-jackson`),\n"
"you cannot inject servlet-based request and response types such as `jakarta.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest` or `jakarta.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse`.\n"
